Package dungeonette.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Door
    Door is an object class which should eventually be used to store door (and possibly lock-and-key) information for any doors placed into the dungeon.
    Environment
    Environment is the parent object class for a multi-floor dungeon.
    Floor
    Floor is an object class which is used to store the information for a single dungeon floor.
    Room
    Object class for the rooms placed into the dungeon.
    Specification
    This class is used for storing the paramets which control the type of dungeon being generated.
    Stairway
    Stairways are the connecting points between two floors.
